24 June 2016Minister of Communications Ms Faith Muthambi will on 25th of June 2016 unveil a Commemorative Plaque of Radio Zibonelo in Khyalestha, Cape Town. It is our mandate as the Department of Communications through the Independent Communications Authority of South Africa (ICASA) and MDDA to ensure that all Municipalities in the country have access to Community media and give them necessary support . Said Muthambi.Details for the event are as follows: Date: 25 June 2016 Time: 10h00- 16h00 Venue: Khayelitsha Thusong Centre Enquiries: Mish Molakeng Contact: 082 469 3997 Issued by GCIS on behalf of the Ministry of Communications